The paper deals with gender classification using facial images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of different descriptors and regions of interest, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the performance of the proposed method on different datasets, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
